The '''Laboratory''' in the [[Cobb's Knob Laboratory]] is where the Knob Goblin mad scientists work. To get inside, you'll need the [[Cobb's Knob lab key]], and at least 30 of your primary stat. Otherwise you get the message:

:As you near the Laboratory, the stench of chemicals and the sounds of science give you pause -- you begin to fear that you're not tough enough to fight here yet.

If you're wearing the [[Knob Goblin Elite Guard Uniform]] [[:Category:Outfits|outfit]], you'll be able to buy things here.

